{"tid":488525,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哥帥：普巴不會真的希望我們的球員受傷","createTime":"2017-12-03T19:39:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T20:16:05.000Z","uid":124292,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5a52f970dc663acda3bd48f9be4f099ed3d294","tid":488525,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T19:39:49.000Z","msg":"在曼城和韋斯咸的比賽結束後，曼市打比成為了媒體關注的焦點，曼城主帥哥迪奧拿對於普巴將缺席本場比賽感到遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n普巴在對陣阿仙奴的比賽中染紅，將因停賽缺席本場比賽。在此之前，他在接受BBC的一檔節目採訪時表示希望曼城的球員遭遇傷病，對此哥帥做出了回應。<br />\n<br />\n「希望沒有人遇到傷病，」哥帥表示。<br />\n<br />\n「我希望普巴能夠參加對陣我們的比賽，因為我喜歡看看我們是否能夠擊敗最強陣容的對手。<br />\n<br />\n「我相信（他說的話）只是一種表達，他不會真的想讓我們的球員受傷。」<br />\n<br />\n人禽之別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898b54265b54b07be82a0fcd9103f0b8799f5945","tid":488525,"uid":104096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T19:43:01.000Z","msg":"氣度"},{"pid":"0c258ee68efc1ca9c4564f9febaf01321fa9f5fb","tid":488525,"uid":150118,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T19:48:06.000Z","msg":"不會想球員受傷,但會踢斷球員的腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e09d549066118cc9bc94657e737a0a8276573ed","tid":488525,"uid":5649,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T19:52:07.000Z","msg":"明串你黑鬼唔識講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce46156dedeeb28dafe3407d49ed03aa578c00c2","tid":488525,"uid":87272,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T20:14:17.000Z","msg":"獌狗真橙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁貴回購自己個冇腦黑鳩"},{"pid":"970858365f7c52dcf5d0c3068efaefe5921f3443","tid":488525,"uid":884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T20:16:05.000Z","msg":"哥迪奧拿真係好有風道"}]}